{"tid":862724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無手足經歷完2014已經睇化？","createTime":"2018-10-15T04:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:45:12.000Z","uid":2542,"like":19,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6225205fbf5c8fb30b94fd09ca874627f1410f43","tid":862724,"uid":2542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"起初雨傘活動好多人都支持同明白，已經唔至係學生一代既想法，部份老一輩都支持。 <br />\n<br />\n但今時今日一兆人工島，係身邊所有年紀大少少的人都支持，我地後生真係少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n個種感覺勁難受，但又無能為力，一枱人食飯12條友，11個都支持，你老母一個口交12條人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n香港人由頭都尾都只係貪錢搵錢走難去香港既一堆垃圾，顧及既只有自己利益。"},{"pid":"bf0a57f20ffc23a3c9afb68d7c44b7c78313834d","tid":862724,"uid":177089,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"我身邊好多廢老都反喎"},{"pid":"2506869d209a798766b34ccc8a74baa1fa07a68e","tid":862724,"uid":2542,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf0a57f20ffc23a3c9afb68d7c44b7c78313834d","tid":862724,"uid":177089,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"我身邊好多廢老都反喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:12:36.000Z","msg":"我個邊無人反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲支持"},{"pid":"3ab140684d5563e9645609964722ddbf1c6c0ca9","tid":862724,"uid":2966,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:57:26.000Z","msg":"唔係叫睇化 係冷感"},{"pid":"4ae149b773ab25382caca9355816dedb62828790","tid":862724,"uid":41524,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"唔好再散播失敗主義"},{"pid":"b7b133a8fb5636861d6a9df41f632cc36489e358","tid":862724,"uid":2542,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4ae149b773ab25382caca9355816dedb62828790","tid":862724,"uid":41524,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"唔好再散播失敗主義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T06:04:25.000Z